  created and pushed the  branch. When the user asked to push
  environment variables, I confirmed that the necessary variables were already
  set for the Preview environment. However, the user noticed that
   was incorrectly set for Production. I promptly
  removed this variable from Production and redeployed the production
  environment to reflect this change. Finally, the user asked for the link to
  the newly configured development environment via the Vercel CLI.
